## 1. Package Version Changes

| Package | PF5 Version | PF6 Version (latest) |
|---------|-------------|---------------------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | `7.x.x` | `8.x.x` (8.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.1) |
| `@patternfly/patternfly` (CSS) | `5.x.x` | `6.x.x` (6.5.2) |

**Victory charts** are now an **optional peer dependency**. Install separately:
- Single package: `victory`
- Or specific packages: `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc.

---

## 2. Codemods & Tooling

### Main Codemods Command
```bash
# Step 1: Dry run (lint-like output)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6

# Step 2: Auto-fix
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix

# Step 3: Cleanup data-codemods attributes (run ONCE after all fixes)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix --only data-codemods-cleanup
```

### Additional Codemod Tools
| Tool | Purpose | Command |
|------|---------|---------|
| **class-name-updater** | Renames `pf-v5-*` CSS classes to `pf-v6-*` in all file types | `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater --v6 --fix <path>` |
| **tokens-update** | Updates CSS variables & React tokens in `.js`/`.tsx` files | Part of main codemods suite |
| **css-vars-updater** | Updates CSS variables in `.css`, `.scss`, `.md` files | `npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <path>` |

---

## 3. CSS Class / Variable / Token Changes

### 3.1 CSS Class Prefix Change
- **All CSS classes**: `pf-v5-` → `pf-v6-`
  - Example: `pf-v5-c-button` → `pf-v6-c-button`
  - Example: `pf-v5-l-flex` → `pf-v6-l-flex`
  - Example: `pf-v5-u-mt-md` → `pf-v6-u-mt-md`
  - Example: `pf-v5-c-page__main` → `pf-v6-c-page__main`

### 3.2 CSS Variable Prefix Change  
- **Component variables**: `--pf-v5-c-*` → `--pf-v6-c-*`
- **Global variables**: `--pf-v5-global--*` → replaced with **design tokens** `--pf-t--global--*`

### 3.3 Design Token System (NEW in PF6)
PatternFly 6 introduces a **design token system**. Old global variables have NEW naming:

| Old PF5 Variable Pattern | New PF6 Token Pattern |
|--------------------------|----------------------|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--md` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--md` |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` | `--pf-t--global--color--*` (semantic) |
| `--pf-v5-global--link--Color` | `--pf-t--global--text--color--link--*` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--sm` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--*` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--*` |

**Key points:**
- NOT a 1:1 mapping — many old variables have been removed or reorganized
- Color variables have NO auto-match → replaced with hot pink (`--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd`) by codemods to flag manual review
- Non-color variables (spacers, font-sizes, box-shadows) get auto-fixed to closest match
- Reference: [All PatternFly Tokens](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens)
- [Removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)

### 3.4 React Tokens (JavaScript)
- **Old pattern**: `import global_FontSize_lg from '@patternfly/react-tokens/dist/esm/global_FontSize_lg'`
- **New pattern**: `import t_global_font_size_lg from '@patternfly/react-tokens/dist/esm/t_global_font_size_lg'`
- All tokens whose value is a `--pf-t` variable are now **prefixed with `t_`**
- Example: `global_link_Color_hover` → `t_global_color_nonstatus_green_clicked` (NOT 1:1 — manual review needed)
- Example: `color_green_10` → `t_color_green_10`

---

## 4. Import Path Changes

### 4.1 Charts (Critical)
Victory-based charts moved to a `victory` subdirectory:
```jsx
// OLD
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// NEW  
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```

### 4.2 Deprecated Components
Components moved to `/deprecated` path:
```jsx
// OLD
import { Modal, Chip, DualListSelector, Tile } from '@patternfly/react-core';

// NEW (deprecated path)
import { Modal, Chip, DualListSelector, Tile } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';
```

### 4.3 Promoted "Next" Components  
Components promoted from `/next` to main:
```jsx
// OLD
import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core/next';

// NEW
import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core';
```

### 4.4 Log Viewer Styles
```jsx
// Updated style import path for log viewer
```

