## 7. Component API Changes

### AccordionContent
- [ ] `isHidden` prop **removed** — visibility now set automatically via `isExpanded` on AccordionItem

### AccordionItem
- [ ] Now renders a `div` wrapper (markup change)

### AccordionToggle
- [ ] `isExpanded` prop **moved** to `AccordionItem`

### Avatar
- [ ] `border` prop **removed** → use `isBordered` prop instead

### Banner
- [ ] `variant` prop **removed** → use `color` or `status` props instead
- [ ] Color values renamed: `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"`

### Button
- [ ] `isActive` prop **renamed** to `isClicked`
- [ ] Icons must be passed to `icon` prop, NOT as children (especially for `variant="plain"`)
- [ ] `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attribute (NOT `aria-disabled`) when `component="button"`
- [ ] `aria-disabled` only renders when `true` (not when false)
- [ ] Button text now wrapped in a `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` div — affects `byText` queries
- [ ] New: `isFavorite` and `isFavorited` props for favorite/star buttons (replaces `StarIcon` as child)

### Card
- [ ] **Removed props**: `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded`
- [ ] Clickable card markup updated

### Checkbox / Radio
- [ ] `isLabelBeforeButton` prop **replaced** with `labelPosition="start"`

### Chip → Label
- [ ] `Chip` deprecated → use `Label`
- [ ] `ChipGroup` deprecated → use `LabelGroup`
- [ ] Chip's `onClick` → Label's `onClose`
- [ ] Chip's `badge` → no direct equivalent

### Content (formerly Text)
- [ ] `Text` → `Content`
- [ ] `TextContent` → `Content`  
- [ ] `TextList` → `Content component="ul"` (or `"ol"`)
- [ ] `TextListItem` → `Content component="li"`
- [ ] `TextVariants` → `ContentVariants`
- [ ] `TextProps` → `ContentProps`
- [ ] `TextListVariants` → removed, use `component` prop
- [ ] `TextListItemVariants` → removed, use `component` prop

### DataListAction
- [ ] `isPlainButtonAction` prop **removed** (wrapper no longer needed)

### Drawer
- [ ] `DrawerHead`: `hasNoPadding` prop **removed**
- [ ] `DrawerContent`/`DrawerPanelContent`/`DrawerSection`: `colorVariant="light-200"` → `colorVariant="secondary"`
- [ ] `DrawerContent`: `colorVariant="no-background"` **removed**; new `"primary"` value added
- [ ] New `DrawerContentColorVariant` enum replaces `DrawerColorVariant` for DrawerContent
- [ ] `DrawerColorVariant.light200` → `DrawerColorVariant.secondary`

### Dropdown (new composable)
- [ ] Default `appendTo` changed to `document.body`

### DualListSelector
- [ ] Old implementation deprecated → import from `/deprecated`
- [ ] New implementation promoted from `/next` to main

### EmptyState ⚠️ MAJOR REFACTOR
- [ ] `EmptyStateHeader` **no longer exported** — use props on `EmptyState` directly
- [ ] `EmptyStateIcon` **no longer exported** — pass icon to `EmptyState`'s `icon` prop
- [ ] Old: `<EmptyState><EmptyStateHeader titleText="..." headingLevel="h4" icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />} /></EmptyState>`
- [ ] New: `<EmptyState titleText="..." headingLevel="h4" icon={CubesIcon}>...</EmptyState>`
- [ ] **Codemods handle partial migration** — manual review likely needed depending on implementation

### ExpandableSection
- [ ] `isActive` prop **removed**

### FormGroup
- [ ] `labelIcon` prop **renamed** to `labelHelp`
- [ ] Recommend using `FormGroupLabelHelp` element for the `labelHelp` prop
- [ ] Wrapper markup changed: `<span className="pf-v6-c-form__group-label-help">` now wraps labelHelp automatically

### FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject
- [ ] Typo fix: `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` → `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject`

### HelperTextItem
- [ ] `hasIcon` prop **removed** — icon auto-renders when `variant` is not "default"
- [ ] `isDynamic` prop **removed**

### JumpLinksItem
- [ ] `href` prop is now **required**
- [ ] Markup has changed

### Label
- [ ] `isOverflowLabel` prop **replaced** with `variant="overflow"`
- [ ] Color values renamed: `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"`

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem
- [ ] Structure changed: instead of many props, everything passed as `children` directly

### LoginMainHeader
- [ ] Markup updated (warning only)

### Masthead ⚠️ STRUCTURAL CHANGES
- [ ] `MastheadBrand` **renamed** to `MastheadLogo`
- [ ] New `MastheadBrand` component is a **wrapper** (different from old)
- [ ] `MastheadToggle` and `MastheadBrand` must now be wrapped in `MastheadMain`
- [ ] `backgroundColor` prop **removed** (theming no longer React-side)
- [ ] Structure: `<Masthead><MastheadMain><MastheadToggle>...</MastheadToggle><MastheadBrand><MastheadLogo>...</MastheadLogo></MastheadBrand></MastheadMain></Masthead>`

### MenuItemAction
- [ ] Markup updated (warning only)

### MenuToggle
- [ ] `splitButtonOptions` prop **replaced** with `splitButtonItems`
- [ ] `SplitButtonOptions` interface deleted; `variant: "action"` no longer supported
