- React 17, react-router 5.3.x

### Branch 1 (`pf-codemods-053126-1055`):
- 1 commit, 16 files changed (90 ins, 56 del)
- NO package.json changes
- Moves Modal to /deprecated (WRONG - code uses new composable API)
- Adds hasBodyWrapper={false} to PageSection/PageBreadcrumb
- 2 remaining pf-v5 refs (same as main, NOT fixed)
- 40 TS errors, build FAILS (same errors as base+PF6 mismatch)
- .cache file committed

### Branch 2 (`semver/goose/053126-1035`):
- 2 commits, 35 files changed (337 ins, 307 del)
- package.json changes: react→18, react-router→7, react-i18next→2.2.3, use-immer→0.1.0 (DOWNGRADES!)
- WRONG: StackItem/SplitItem component prop misuse (passes JSX elements, should be string)
- WRONG: Tooltip appendTo="inline" (not supported)
- Fixed pf-v5 CSS refs (0 remaining)
- Button icon prop migration, SelectList additions, appendTo="inline"
- 40 TS errors, build FAILS (webpack shared module validation)
- Excessive unrelated package version changes that break build

## Phases
- [x] Phase 1: Research PF5→PF6 migration requirements
- [x] Phase 2: Establish comparison baseline
- [x] Phase 3: Branch-by-branch analysis
- [ ] Phase 4: Generate HTML report


