          <td class="loser-cell">Not addressed ❌</td>
          <td class="winner-cell">~5 instances migrated ✅</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>semver/goose example (correct)</h4>
    <pre><code><span class="code-del">// BEFORE
&lt;Button variant={ButtonVariant.link}&gt;
  {iface.name}
  &lt;Icon className="..." /&gt;
&lt;/Button&gt;</span>

<span class="code-add">// AFTER (correct PF6 pattern)
&lt;Button variant={ButtonVariant.link} icon={&lt;Icon className="..." /&gt;}&gt;
  {iface.name}
&lt;/Button&gt;</span></code></pre>

    <p>This is a legitimate PF6 migration change. The button <code>icon</code> prop is the correct PF6 pattern per official docs.</p>

    <div class="winner-badge">🏆 Winner: semver/goose — correctly migrated button icons</div>
  </div>
</details>

