<!-- appendTo -->
<details id="appendto">
  <summary>📌 appendTo Changes <span class="badge badge-orange" style="margin-left:auto">Mixed — semver/goose partially correct</span></summary>
  <div class="details-body">
    <h4>What PF6 requires</h4>
    <p>PF6 changed the default <code>appendTo</code> for Popper-based components (Dropdown, Select, Popover) to <code>document.body</code>. For testing, <code>appendTo="inline"</code> can be used. However, not all components support the <code>"inline"</code> string value.</p>

    <table class="comparison-mini">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Component</th><th>Supports appendTo="inline"?</th><th>semver/goose usage</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Popover</td>
          <td class="winner-cell">Yes ✅</td>
          <td class="winner-cell">Correct ✅</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Dropdown (popperProps)</td>
          <td class="winner-cell">Yes ✅</td>
          <td class="winner-cell">Correct ✅</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Tooltip</td>
          <td class="loser-cell">No ❌ (only HTMLElement | function)</td>
          <td class="loser-cell">WRONG — EditButtonWithTooltip.tsx uses appendTo="inline" ❌</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
